The video clip shows Biden at a signing: House Speaker Nancy Pelosi, and Vice President Kamala Harris standing behind him.
A text caption near Biden reads: I don’t know what I’m signing," and a caption below Harris reads, "Sign it anyways."
The original video clip: visible on VOA News and PBS News Hour, shows Biden signing his first documents as president of the United States.
Rob Maher: an audio forensic analysis expert, analyzed the audio in the video and stated that he did not detect any utterance by Biden saying, "I don't know what I'm signing here."
